<doc id="1138082" wikidata="Q3835187" url="?curid=1138082" title="Live Heroes">
<text>Live Heroes is a compilation album recorded by Nico with the Blue Orchids, the Invisible Girls and Samarkand (Mahamad Hadi). The tracks &quot;Heroes&quot;, &quot;Valley of the Kings&quot; and &quot;Femme Fatale&quot; were recorded live at Saltlageret in Copenhagen on October 5, 1982, while the tracks &quot;Procession&quot; and &quot;All Tomorrow&#x27;s Parties&quot; were recorded during a studio session with the Invisible Girls and Martin Hannett.

==Track listing==
