*The Invisible Girls – arrangements, performers 
*Samarkand (Mahamad Hadi) – backing band 
*The Blue Orchids – backing band 
*Martin Hannett – producer 
*Robert Speiden – mastering
*Murray Brenman – design
*Arthur Marko – design concept 
*Stephen Kaplan – design concept

