<doc id="1138094" wikidata="Q1991754" url="?curid=1138094" title="Aznar Galíndez II">
<text>Aznar Galíndez II was a Count of Aragón (867–893), son and successor of Galindo Aznárez I.

Aznar married Oneca, daughter of the king of Pamplona, Garcia Iñíguez, and had:
*Galindo Aznárez II
*García
*Sancha, wife of Muhammad al-Tawil, wali of Huesca

Aznar died in 893.

